                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5566" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1405</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9212 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Gorenje“命悬一线”：新东家海信能否助其“渡劫”成功？（A）（B）（C）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">If Hisense Can Help Gorenje Recover from Predicament？(A）（B）（C）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘素，刘海玲，陈志军</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海信</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家电行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海信；跨国并购；科层制；组织变革；组织设计；整合策略；2021百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hisense; Cross border M &amp; A; Bureaucracy; Organizational change; Organization design; Integration strategy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">由于面临着成本压力和激烈的市场竞争，有着70年历史的欧洲白色家电巨头Gorenje公司2017年利润大幅下滑84%，随后开始寻求战略合作伙伴。2018年7月份，海信完成了对Gorenje 95.42%股权的收购。这无疑能为海信进一步扩展欧洲家电市场打下坚实基础。然而令海信措手不及的是，刚办完交接手续，Gorenje就因资金链断裂等各种新老问题，站在了生与死的边缘。要想“盘活”它，海信必须立即启动对Gorenje整个公司的变革方案，重新进行组织设计，以达到提高竞争力的目的。一旦要进行变革，就会直接影响到1万多名Gorenje欧洲员工的切身利益。人生地不熟的海信一来就要给习惯了科层制管理体系的Gorenje动“大手术”，是过度自信还是迫于无奈？海信的组织变革方案能得到欧洲员工的认同吗？海信真有能力帮助Gorenje“渡劫”成功吗？一场中西合璧的组织大变革正在上演。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Faced with cost pressure and fierce market competition, Gorenje, a 70 year old European kitchen appliance giant, saw its profit drop by 84% in 2017, and then began to seek strategic partners. In July 2018, Hisense completed the acquisition of Gorenje’s 95.42% equity. This will undoubtedly lay a solid foundation for Hisense to further expand the European home appliance market. However, what surprised Hisense was that just after the handover procedures, Gorenje was in deep crisis because of various new and old problems such as the rupture of capital chain. In order to &quot;revitalize&quot; it, Hisense must immediately start the reform plan for the whole company and redesign its organization to improve its competitiveness. Once a change was made, it would directly affect the vital interests of more than 10000 Gorenje employees in Europe. Hisense, who was not familiar with Gorenje’s situation, was going to have a &quot;big operation&quot; on Gorenje, who was used to the hierarchical management system. Was it in overconfidence or helplessness? Could Hisense&#39;s organizational change plan be recognized by European employees? Did Hisense really have the ability to help Gorenje’s survival? A combination of Chinese and western organizational change was on stage.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《国际企业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科层制结构和扁平化结构 并购</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-10</td>
